         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">9/7/79. ¶  ¶ By the Ship "Kent" next week, dear and honored Sir, I have occasion to send a scientific consignment to Dr Sonder in Hamburg, and will forward with it  ¶ all my specimens of Epilobium fro...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.07.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edmond Boissier</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>9/7/79.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By the Ship "Kent" next week, dear and honored Sir, I have occasion to send a scientific consignment to Dr Sonder in Hamburg, and will forward with it <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">all my specimens of Epilobium from Australia and New Zealand as loan</hi>
               </seg> to your excellent son. It seems useless to send also my extra australian Epilobia, as similar material of far greater extent will be available to him in European Museums. When he has used these specimens, I like them returned to Dr Sonder.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I discovered a leafless Statice at Shark Bay on the West Australian coast and described it as S. salicorniacea in the XI vol. of the Fragmenta.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B78.03.01, p. 7.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
